Direct copy of http://github.com/mattmatt/run_later/tree/master by Ported to Rails by Mathias Meyer (http://paperplanes.de) added one line for sinatra

Released under the MIT license


Usage:

require 'rubygems'
require 'sinatra'
require 'run_later'

get '/' do
  run_later do
    #some task that you don't want to block.
    sleep 20
  end
  "Hello World"
end